a case of puppy love. Her dog is crazy about him.
</P>
<P>
   ''Oliver is a great judge of character,'' Heather Mills told
reporters Wednesday as she posed with the 3-year-old terrier at the
launch of a campaign to encourage better treatment of pets. ''He
and Paul get on very well together.''
</P>
<P>
