achievement, but to keep a rock 'n' roll marriage going for that
long is unbelievable,'' Mills said. ''She did a wonderful job with
Paul and her family and I have got nothing but admiration for
her.''
</P>
<P>
   McCartney confirmed in March that he and Mills were dating.
